            {"en": "If we had known about the problem, we would have fixed it immediately.", "de": "Wenn wir von dem Problem gewusst hatten, hatten wir es sofort behoben.", "fr": "Si nous avions su le probleme, nous l'aurions resolu immediatement.", "it": "Se avessimo saputo del problema, lo avremmo risolto immediatamente.", "es": "Si hubieramos sabido del problema, lo habriamos arreglado inmediatamente.", "tr": "Sorunu bilseydik hemen cozerdik."},
            {"en": "If he had not missed the flight, he would have attended the conference.", "de": "Wenn er den Flug nicht verpasst hatte, hatte er an der Konferenz teilgenommen.", "fr": "S'il n'avait pas rate le vol, il aurait assiste a la conference.", "it": "Se non avesse perso il volo, avrebbe partecipato alla conferenza.", "es": "Si no hubiera perdido el vuelo, habria asistido a la conferencia.", "tr": "Ucagi kacirmasaydi konferansa katilirdi."},
