            {"prompt": "I expected him to apologize, but he ___.", "answer": "didn't", "hint": "didn't = yapmadi (ellipsis)"},
            {"prompt": "'Will it rain?' 'I don't think ___.'", "answer": "so", "hint": "so = olumsuz yerine koyma"},
